OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FE-bike rider killed in     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcrash was kindest boy - mum
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A teenager who died when his e-bike    
OL,6, collided with an ambulance after he was
OL,7, followed by police was "the most       
OL,8, sweetest, kindest boy ever", his mother
OL,9, has said.                              
OL,11,FSaul Cookson, 15, was being followed by
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) traffic
OL,13,Fofficers in Salford on Thursday until  
OL,14,Fbollards blocked their vehicle's path. 
OL,16,FHis e-bike then collided with the North
OL,17,FWest Ambulance Service (NWAS) vehicle. 
OL,19,FEmma Frendo said her son had been      
OL,20,F"loved by all that met him".           
